#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/rest-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When using `quarkus-rest-client`, users can use the `quarkus-keycloak-admin-rest-client` to administer the target Keycloak instance\n"
